### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/health

### Speaker list
GET http://127.0.0.1:8787/speakers

### Exact TTS
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/speak
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "こんにちは。これはテスト音声です。",
  "speaker_id": 3,
  "save_file": true
}

### Bits alert with message
POST http://127.0.0.1:8787/alert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_type": "bits",
  "name": "SeoyaFan",
  "amount": 500,
  "message": "今日も配信ありがとう！無理しないでね。",
  "speaker_id": 3,
  "with_sfx": true,
  "save_file": true
}
